## Cost & Latency Comparison

| Metric | Current | Proposed | Improvement |
|--------|---------|----------|-------------|
| LLM Calls per Query | 2 | 1 | 50% reduction |
| Tokens per Query | 1500-2500 | 800-1200 | ~50% reduction |
| Latency (p95) | 800ms | 300-400ms | 50-60% faster |
| Cost per Query | $0.003-0.006 | $0.001-0.003 | 50-60% cheaper |
| Code Complexity | High (469-line prompt + validation) | Low (simple rules) | 50% less code |
| Reliability | 70% valid charts | 90%+ valid charts | 20%+ improvement |

